<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4807200>
    dc:description "FIGURES 36–38. Male genitalia of Psoricoptera spp. 36, P. minutignatha sp. nov., holotype, slide no. ZML19287, 36a–36b, showing variations in affiliated plate (36a) and saccus (36b), paratype, slide no. ZML19320; 37–38, P. proximikawabei sp. nov., paratypes, slide nos. ZML19299, SYW05489. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4807200/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4807196>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31–34. Male genitalia of Psoricoptera spp. 31, P. curva sp. nov., holotype, slide no. ZML19302; 32–34, P. gibbosella, slide nos. ZML19307, ZML19286, ZML19318. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4807196/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4807198>
    dc:description "FIGURE 35. Male genitalia of Psoricoptera latignathosa, slide no. ZML19313, 35a–35g, enlarged view of various-shaped uncus and gnathos, slide nos. ZML19331, SYW05214, ZH07244, ZML19334, ZML19333, ZML19305, ZML19311. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4807198/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4807204>
    dc:description "FIGURE 39. Male genitalia of Psoricoptera speciosella, slide no. ZML19339, 39a–39d, enlarged view of various-shaped uncus and gnathos, slide nos. ZML19341, ZML19319, ZML19328, ZML19342. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4807204/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

